{"type":"message","id":"dfc2b221","parentId":"609b9b48","timestamp":"2026-03-22T03:04:28.152Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"看起来页面没有加载正确的文档内容。我得到的是整个专题页面的导航内容，而不是具体的文档内容。这可能是因为点击没有真正触发导航。\n\n让我尝试一种不同的方法：使用web_fetch直接抓取文档页面。但首先我需要找到\"文本字段\"等文档的具体URL。\n\n让我先通过JavaScript获取所有文档链接。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_ca17853c24e24f1c8ece936c","name":"browser","arguments":{"action":"act","kind":"evaluate","fn":"() => {\n  // 获取所有文档链接\n  const links = [];\n  const allLinks = document.querySelectorAll('a[href*=\"knowledge\"]');\n  \n  for (const link of allLinks) {\n    const text = link.textContent.trim();\n    const href = link.href;\n    \n    // 匹配目标文档\n    const targets = ['文本字段', '整数字段', '小数字段', '日期字段', '基础资料字段', '单据体'];\n    if (targets.some(t => text.includes(t))) {\n      links.push({\n        text,\n        href\n      });\n    }\n  }\n  \n  return JSON.stringify(links.slice(0, 20));\n}"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":10105,"output":230,"cacheRead":59328,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":69663,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774148656511}}
