{"type":"message","id":"e57738ad","parentId":"b6776f17","timestamp":"2026-03-22T03:06:28.779Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"这次我获取到了页面内容，但仍然是专题页面的导航内容，而不是\"文本字段\"文档的具体内容。看起来URL参数没有起作用，或者页面需要特定的交互才能加载文档内容。\n\n让我尝试另一种方法：直接通过JavaScript触发文档加载。我注意到之前获取到的元素有ID，让我尝试直接点击这些元素。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_3641f46e44ae4df0a0bea800","name":"browser","arguments":{"action":"act","kind":"evaluate","fn":"() => {\n  // 查找并点击文本字段文档\n  const allCategoryDivs = document.querySelectorAll('.all-category');\n  \n  for (const div of allCategoryDivs) {\n    if (div.textContent && div.textContent.includes('文本字段') && !div.textContent.includes('多语言')) {\n      div.click();\n      return '点击了文本字段 (all-category)';\n    }\n  }\n  \n  return '未找到文本字段';\n}"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":5522,"output":183,"cacheRead":55552,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":61257,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774148778072}}
